reviewText: Very instructive, but not for everyone.  A very deep teaching....

Perry Stone once again came up it seems with all the knowledge and wisdom he got from the best sources! However the first disc stopped towards the end we thought it's the devil hindering us from hearing the most important part of the message that was supposed come because when we checked it did not have any scratches on it or anything....Besides of all it's worth learning and having a open eye on purging the house thru these DVDs, i recommend it !!!
